  token: {{authToken}}
}

docs {
  # Get All Categories
  
  Retrieves all inventory categories with optional filtering.
  
  ## Query Parameters
  - `isActive` (boolean, optional): Filter by active status
  
  ## Response
  Returns array of category objects.
}
